        "p      norm for matrices",
        "=====  ============================",
        "None   2-norm, computed directly using the ``SVD``",
        "'fro'  Frobenius norm",
        "inf    max(sum(abs(x), axis=1))",
        "-inf   min(sum(abs(x), axis=1))",
